## ğŸ”‘ Setup

1. **Get your Gemini API key** from [Google AI Studio](https://makersuite.google.com/app/apikey)

2. **Set your API key:**

   ```bash
   # Windows PowerShell
   $env:GEMINI_API_KEY = "your_api_key_here"
   
   # Linux/Mac
   export GEMINI_API_KEY="your_api_key_here"
   ```

3. **Run NexShell:**

   ```bash
   nexshell
   ```

## ğŸ® Usage

### Quick Start

```bash
nexshell
```

### ğŸ’¡ Commands

| Command | Description |
|---------|-------------|
| `/mode [type]` | Switch AI mode (normal/code/creative/concise) |
| `/cmd [command]` | Execute system commands |
| `/save` | Export conversation to file |
| `/stats` | View session statistics |
| `/history` | Show conversation summary |
| `/clear` | Clear conversation history |
| `/help` | Display help information |
| `/exit` or `/quit` | Exit NexShell |

### ï¿½ AI Modes

- **ğŸ¤– Normal** - Balanced AI for general conversations
- **ğŸ’» Code** - Programming expert with detailed examples
- **ğŸ¨ Creative** - Imaginative and artistic responses
- **âš¡ Concise** - Brief, bullet-point answers

